item.title: CVE-2023-22478|2023-01-14T00:22:54.146Z -- kubeoperator -- kubepi
item.description: KubePi is a modern Kubernetes panel. The API interfaces with unauthorized entities and may leak sensitive information. This issue has been patched in version 1.6.4. There are currently no known workarounds.
